Todd Slater is recognized as one of the top independent film and media consultants in Hollywood. Areas of expertise include financial modeling, media and film transactions, negotiation of rights and distribution, and the structuring of media financing. Todd Slater is the former Executive Vice President at Philip Anschuz's film company (Anschutz ...            
